items: Passal . A generous person , and ingenious .
Maldrin . A deserving Gentleman , and friend to Passal .
Sr. Ral. Nonsuch . A publick ridiculous pretender , and a Luxuriast .
Bowser . Their Friend , and lover of Sport .
Plodwell . A Lawyer , and of a handsome Character .
Breakbond . A wilde Gentleman , obliging the Sex of Women , and of a generous character , except in payment of Bonds .
Pricknote . An hypocritical Sectary and Knave interested in Sir Ral. Nonsuch .
Jocalin . A lover of Pleasure and Ingenuity .
Quickthrift . A Lady of Wit , but proud and covetous , courted by Plodwell .
Luce : A pretended Miss to Sir Ralph Nonsuch .
